op_master_id: (SELECT KI.KI AS KI, K.KICD AS KICD, RTRIM(K.KCOD) AS KCOD, K.KNMX AS KNMX, K.KNAM AS KNAM, K.KNLD AS KNLD, K.KOCD AS KOCD, K.KATT AS KATT, K.GSW1 AS GSW1, K.GSW2 AS GSW2, K.SY01 AS SY01, K.SY02 AS SY02, K.SY03 AS SY03, K.SY04 AS SY04, K.SY05 AS SY05, K.SY06 AS SY06, K.SY07 AS SY07, K.SY08 AS SY08, K.KE02 AS KE02, K.KT02 AS KT02, K.KB02 AS KB02, K.BKE01 AS BKE01, K.SG02 AS SG02, K.PJ02 AS PJ02, :DM1 AS UF12, :DM2 AS UF22, :DM3 AS UF32, K.KJ02 AS KJ02, K.KS02 AS KS02, K.TK02 AS TK02, K.BTK01 AS BTK01, K.BTKE01 AS BTKE01, K.TKE01 AS TKE01, K.STK01 AS STK01, K.KK01 AS KK01 FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI JOIN dbo.KNAME AS K ON K.KESN = KI.KESN)

(select KI.KI AS KI, Z.KICD AS KICD, RTRIM(Z.ECOD) AS ECOD, RTRIM(K.KCOD) AS KCOD, K.KOCD AS KOCD, K.KNMX AS KNMX, K.KNAM AS KNAM, K.KATT AS KATT, CAST( CASE WHEN E.ENSG = 1 THEN E.ENAM WHEN E.TCOD IS NULL THEN '' ELSE ISNULL((SELECT Z.TNAM FROM dbo.ZMTKY Z WHERE Z.KESN = E.KESN AND Z.TCOD = E.TCOD), '') END AS CHAR(20) ) AS ENAM, 0 as K000 from AEXP.A_KI as KI join dbo.EDZAN as Z on Z.KESN = KI.KESN join dbo.KNAME as K on K.KESN = Z.KESN and K.KICD = Z.KICD join dbo.ENAME as E on E.KESN = Z.KESN and E.KICD = Z.KICD and E.ECOD = Z.ECOD)
(SELECT KI.KI AS KI, RTRIM(B.BCOD) AS BCOD, B.BNAM AS BNAM, B.BNLD BNLD, B.BFLG AS BFLG FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI JOIN dbo.BNAME AS B ON B.KESN = KI.KESN AND B.BFLG = '0')

(SELECT KI.KI AS KI,
 RTRIM(Z.BCOD) AS BCOD,
 Z.KICD AS KICD,
 B.BNAM AS BNAM,
 RTRIM(K.KCOD) AS KCOD,
 K.KOCD AS KOCD,
 K.KNMX AS KNMX,
 K.KNAM AS KNAM,
 K.KATT AS KATT,
 Z.R000 AS R000,
 Z.S000 AS S000,
 Z.R010 AS R010,
 Z.S010 AS S010,
 Z.R020 AS R020,
 Z.S020 AS S020,
 Z.R030 AS R030,
 Z.S030 AS S030,
 CASE WHEN O.S035 = 1 THEN Z.R035 ELSE 0 END AS R035,
 CASE WHEN O.S035 = 1 THEN Z.S035 ELSE 0 END AS S035,
 Z.R040 AS R040,
 Z.S040 AS S040,
 Z.R050 AS R050,
 Z.S050 AS S050,
 Z.R060 AS R060,
 Z.S060 AS S060,
 CASE WHEN O.S065 = 1 THEN Z.R065 ELSE 0 END AS R065,
 CASE WHEN O.S065 = 1 THEN Z.S065 ELSE 0 END AS S065,
 Z.R070 AS R070,
 Z.S070 AS S070,
 Z.R080 AS R080,
 Z.S080 AS S080,
 Z.R090 AS R090,
 Z.S090 AS S090,
 CASE WHEN O.S095 = 1 THEN Z.R095 ELSE 0 END AS R095,
 CASE WHEN O.S095 = 1 THEN Z.S095 ELSE 0 END AS S095,
 Z.R100 AS R100,
 Z.S100 AS S100,
 Z.R110 AS R110,
 Z.S110 AS S110,
 Z.R120 AS R120,
 Z.S120 AS S120,
 CASE WHEN O.S125 = 1 THEN Z.R125 ELSE 0 END AS R125,
 CASE WHEN O.S125 = 1 THEN Z.S125 ELSE 0 END AS S125 
FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI 
JOIN DBO.BKZAN AS Z ON Z.KESN = KI.KESN 
JOIN DBO.BNAME AS B ON B.KESN = Z.KESN AND B.BCOD = Z.BCOD 
JOIN DBO.KNAME AS K ON K.KESN = Z.KESN AND K.KICD = Z.KICD 
JOIN DBO.SEIOPT AS O ON O.KESN = Z.KESN AND O.UCOD = 10000 AND O.ITEM = 0 
WHERE
    KI.KI IN (0, 1, 2, 3)
)
(SELECT RTRIM(T.TRCD) AS TRCD, T.TRMX AS TRMX, T.TRNAM AS TRNAM, T.RNLD AS RNLD FROM dbo.TRNAM T)

(SELECT TR.TRCD, TR.ZIP, TR.ADDR1, TR.ADDR2, TR.TEL, TR.FAX, FR.MEIGI, FR.MEIGIK, SK.SKBKIND, FR.YOKIN_TYP, FR.KOUZA, FR.TESUU, FR.SOUKIN, FR.BANK_CD, FR.SITEN_ID, SH.SIHARAIDD, SH.SKIJITUDD, SH.V_YAKUJO FROM SS_TORI TR JOIN (SELECT TRCD, MIN(HJCD) AS HJCDMIN FROM SS_TORI GROUP BY TRCD) TRH ON TR.TRCD = TRH.TRCD AND TR.HJCD = TRH.HJCDMIN JOIN SS_TSHOH TS ON TS.TRCD = TR.TRCD AND TS.HJCD = TR.HJCD AND TS.SHO_ID = 1 JOIN SS_SHOHO SH ON SH.SHINO = TS.SHINO JOIN SS_SKUBN SK ON SK.SKBNCOD = SH.SKBNCOD JOIN SS_FRIGIN FR ON FR.TRCD = TR.TRCD AND FR.HJCD = TR.HJCD AND FR.GIN_ID = 1 WHERE LEN(TR.TRCD) < 13)

(SELECT DISTINCT
    kesn,
    ki,
    CAST(CAST(symd as CHAR(8)) AS DATE) as symd,
    CAST(CAST(eymd as CHAR(8)) AS DATE) as eymd
FROM
    (SELECT
        ki.KESN,
        v.*
    FROM aexp.a_ki ki
    JOIN aexp.a_volum2 v ON
        ki.ki = v.ki
    WHERE
        RIGHT(v.symd, 2) <> '00' AND
        RIGHT(v.eymd, 2) <> '00'
    ) t
)

(SELECT
    kmk.kesn,
    RTRIM(kmk.kicd) AS kicd,
    RTRIM(kmk.kcod) AS kcod,
    kmk.knmx,
    kmk.katt
FROM aexp.a_ki AS ki
JOIN kname AS kmk ON 
    kmk.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT 
    bmn.kesn, 
    RTRIM(bmn.bcod) AS bcod, 
    bmn.bnam, 
    RTRIM(stb.bcd1) AS bcd1 
FROM aexp.a_ki AS ki 
JOIN bname AS bmn ON 
    bmn.kesn = ki.kesn 
JOIN sstbl AS stb ON 
    bmn.kesn = stb.kesn 
    AND bmn.bcod = stb.bcd2 
WHERE 
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3) 
)

(SELECT
    sbmn.kesn,
    sbmn.sbcd,
    sbname.bnam AS sbnam,
    zbmn.bcod,
    zbmn.bnam
FROM aexp.a_ki ki
JOIN sbtbl AS sbmn ON
    ki.kesn = sbmn.kesn
JOIN bname AS sbname ON
    sbmn.kesn = sbname.kesn AND
    sbmn.sbcd = sbname.bcod AND
    sbname.bflg = 1
JOIN bname AS zbmn ON
    sbmn.kesn = zbmn.kesn AND
    sbmn.bcod = zbmn.bcod AND
    zbmn.bflg = 0
WHERE
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT
    kmk.kesn,
    kmk.sptn,
    kmk.szkm
FROM aexp.a_ki ki
JOIN sczkm kmk ON
    kmk.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    kmk.skbn = 0 AND
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT
    bmn.kesn,
    bmn.sptn,
    bmn.szbm
FROM aexp.a_ki AS ki
JOIN sczbm AS bmn ON
    bmn.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    bmn.skbn = 0 and
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT
    eda.kesn,
    RTRIM(eda.kicd) AS kicd,
    RTRIM(eda.ecod) AS ecod,
    eda.enam
FROM aexp.a_ki AS ki
JOIN ename as eda ON
    eda.kesn = ki.kesn
WHERE
    ki.ki in (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

(SELECT KI.KI AS KI,
 RTRIM(Y.BCOD) AS BCOD,
 Y.KICD AS KICD,
 B.BNAM AS BNAM,
 RTRIM(K.KCOD) AS KCOD,
 K.KOCD AS KOCD,
 K.KNMX AS KNMX,
 K.KNAM AS KNAM,
 K.KATT AS KATT,
 Y.Y010 AS Y010,
 Y.Y020 AS Y020,
 Y.Y030 AS Y030,
 CASE WHEN O.S035 = 1 THEN Y.Y035 ELSE 0 END AS Y035,
 Y.Y040 AS Y040,
 Y.Y050 AS Y050,
 Y.Y060 AS Y060,
 CASE WHEN O.S065 = 1 THEN Y.Y065 ELSE 0 END AS Y065,
 Y.Y070 AS Y070,
 Y.Y080 AS Y080,
 Y.Y090 AS Y090,
 CASE WHEN O.S095 = 1 THEN Y.Y095 ELSE 0 END AS Y095,
 Y.Y100 AS Y100,
 Y.Y110 AS Y110,
 Y.Y120 AS Y120,
 CASE WHEN O.S125 = 1 THEN Y.Y125 ELSE 0 END AS Y125 
FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI 
JOIN DBO.:BKYSN AS Y ON Y.KESN = KI.KESN 
JOIN DBO.BNAME AS B ON B.KESN = Y.KESN AND B.BCOD = Y.BCOD 
JOIN DBO.KNAME AS K ON K.KESN = Y.KESN AND K.KICD = Y.KICD 
JOIN DBO.SEIOPT AS O ON O.KESN = Y.KESN AND O.UCOD = 10000 AND O.ITEM = 0 
WHERE
    KI.KI IN (0, 1, 2, 3)
)

 Z.R060 AS R060,
 Z.S060 AS S060,

 CASE WHEN O.S065 = 1 THEN Z.S065 ELSE 0 END AS S065,
 Z.R070 AS R070,
 Z.S070 AS S070,
 Z.R080 AS R080,

JOIN DBO.BKEZAN AS Z ON Z.KESN = KI.KESN 
JOIN DBO.BNAME AS B ON B.KESN = Z.KESN AND B.BCOD = Z.BCOD 
JOIN DBO.KNAME AS K ON K.KESN = Z.KESN AND K.KICD = Z.KICD 
JOIN DBO.SEIOPT AS O ON O.KESN = Z.KESN AND O.UCOD = 10000 AND O.ITEM = 0

(SELECT KI.KI AS KI,
 RTRIM(Y.BCOD) AS BCOD,

 K.KNMX AS KNMX,
 K.KNAM AS KNAM,

 Y.Y010 AS Y010,
 Y.Y020 AS Y020,

 CASE WHEN O.S035 = 1 THEN Y.Y035 ELSE 0 END AS Y035,
 Y.Y040 AS Y040,
 Y.Y050 AS Y050,

(SELECT KI.KI AS KI, RTRIM(B.BCOD) AS BCOD, B.BNAM AS BNAM, B.BNLD BNLD, B.BFLG AS BFLG FROM AEXP.A_KI AS KI JOIN dbo.BNAME AS B ON B.KESN = KI.KESN AND B.BFLG = '1')

(SELECT
    kesn,
    dkei,
    dseq,
    sseq,
    CAST(CAST(dymd as CHAR(8)) AS DATE) as dymd,
    dcno,
    rbmn,
    rkmk,
    reda,
    sbmn,
    skmk,
    seda,
    valu
FROM
    (SELECT
        h.dymd,
        h.dcno,
        s.*
    FROM sjdat_h AS h
    JOIN sjdat AS s ON
        h.kesn = s.kesn AND
        h.dseq = s.dseq AND
        h.dkei = s.dkei
    WHERE
        h.delf = 0 AND
        h.kday <> 0 AND
        (h.sflg = 0 OR h.sflg = 1) AND
        h.bflg = 0
    ) AS t
)
